title: Aksel Lund Svindel's message for Lausanne 2020 and a Pakistani skier
description: Two-time Olympic champion alpine skier Aksel Lund Svindal gives a good luck message to those competing at the Winter Youth Olympic Games in Lausanne. Plus, Pakistani alpine skier Mia Freudweiler on her hope to inspire more women to ski in her country and a last question with Lausanne mascot Yodli.
